node.text: REMINDER: Don’t let that ONE bad thing that happened today ruin your mood for the rest of the day!  We tend to focus on the pain and forget the joys of life so easily. Let’s change that 💛

You have the strength and ability to create a new normal, BELIEVE IT WITH ALL YOUR HEART AND MIND and then go do it! Radhi'.

node.text: Ooooh this ones a tough one BUT SO TRUE! You know why, because your pain is real to YOU and their pain is real to THEM. We disqualify others pain just because we feel ours is worse..instead of seeing one right and one wrong I’ve found working through each separately in your mind and just taking time to understand how and why the other person could feel that way has always helped me. DON’T GET ME WRONG my first reaction is usually Me feeling like I’m absolutely right (I’m not stubborn at all 😂😂😅🙄) but after I break it down and really think about them separately I see there really are two sides to most stories!
